Package: ISCAM
Title: Companion to the Book "Investigating Statistical Concepts, Applications, and Methods"
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Beth", "Chance", email = "bchance@calpoly.edu", role = c("cre", "cph")),
    person("Visruth", "Srimath Kandali", email = "visruth@gmail.com", role = c("aut"), comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0005-9097-0688"))
    )
Description: Introductory statistics methods to accompany "Investigating Statistical Concepts, Applications, and Methods" by Beth Chance & Allan Rossman. Tools to introduce statistical concepets with a focus on simulation approaches. Functions are verbose, designed to provide ample output for students to understand what each function does. Additionally, most functions are accompanied with plots. The package is designed to be used in an educational setting.
